rfcmarkup (1.23)  

  * Removed 'relnotes' from the source, maintaining only the
    separate changelog.

  * Added features proposed by Julian Reschke:

    * Header tags for each section header, with header level
      matching section sub-level.  Used with Firefox' document
      map plugin this makes navigation very easy.

    * Added some css styles to support the use of header tags

    * Cleaned out unused script code

